### ============================================
### 🧪 TEST CUSTOMERS API - SuperMarketMini
### ============================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@adminToken = 
@cashierToken = 
@managerToken = 

### ============================================
### 🔐 1. LOGIN (Chạy trước để lấy token)
### ============================================

### 1.1 Login Admin
# @name loginAdmin
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "Admin@123"
}

### 1.2 Login Cashier
# @name loginCashier
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "cashier",
  "password": "Cashier@123"
}

### 1.3 Login Manager
# @name loginManager
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "manager",
  "password": "Manager@123"
}

### ============================================
### 👥 2. GET ALL CUSTOMERS
### ============================================

### 2.1 Admin - Get All Customers (Expected: 200 OK)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/customers
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 2.2 Admin - Get Customers with Pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/customers?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 2.3 Admin - Search Customers by Keyword
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/customers?keyword=Nguyen
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 2.4 Cashier - Get Customers (Expected: 403 Forbidden - cần customers.view permission)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/customers
Authorization: Bearer {{cashierToken}}

### 2.5 No Token - Get Customers (Expected: 401 Unauthorized)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/customers

### ============================================
### 🔍 3. GET CUSTOMER BY ID
### ============================================

### 3.1 Admin - Get Customer by ID (Expected: 200 OK or 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/customers/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 3.2 Admin - Get Non-existent Customer (Expected: 404 Not Found)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/customers/99999
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ============================================
### ➕ 4. CREATE CUSTOMER
### ============================================

### 4.1 Admin - Create Customer Success (Expected: 200 OK)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/customers
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "fullName": "Nguyen Van Test",
  "phone": "0909123456",
  "email": "test.customer@example.com"
}

### 4.2 Admin - Create Customer without Name (Expected: 400 Bad Request)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/customers
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "phone": "0909123457"
}

### 4.3 Admin - Create Customer with Invalid Email (Expected: 400 Bad Request)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/customers
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "fullName": "Test Customer",
  "email": "invalid-email"
}

### 4.4 Admin - Create Customer with Duplicate Phone (Expected: 400 Bad Request)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/customers
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "fullName": "Duplicate Phone Test",
  "phone": "0909123456"
}

### 4.5 Cashier - Create Customer (Expected: 403 Forbidden)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/customers
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{cashierToken}}

{
  "fullName": "Cashier Customer Test",
  "phone": "0909123458"
}

### ============================================
### ✏️ 5. UPDATE CUSTOMER
### ============================================

### 5.1 Admin - Update Customer (Expected: 200 OK)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/customers/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "fullName": "Updated Customer Name",
  "phone": "0909876543",
  "email": "updated@example.com"
}

### 5.2 Admin - Update Non-existent Customer (Expected: 404 Not Found)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/customers/99999
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "fullName": "Non Existent"
}

### 5.3 Admin - Update with Duplicate Phone (Expected: 400 Bad Request)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/customers/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "phone": "0909123456"
}

### ============================================
### 🗑️ 6. DELETE CUSTOMER
### ============================================

### 6.1 Admin - Delete Customer (Expected: 200 OK - nếu không có hóa đơn)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/customers/2
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 6.2 Admin - Delete Customer with Invoices (Expected: 400 Bad Request)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/customers/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 6.3 Admin - Delete Non-existent Customer (Expected: 404 Not Found)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/customers/99999
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ============================================
### 📜 7. GET CUSTOMER INVOICES
### ============================================

### 7.1 Admin - Get Customer Invoices (Expected: 200 OK)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/customers/1/invoices
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 7.2 Admin - Get Customer Invoices with Pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/customers/1/invoices?page=1&pageSize=5
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 7.3 Admin - Get Invoices for Non-existent Customer (Expected: 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/customers/99999/invoices
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ============================================
### 🔎 8. QUICK SEARCH CUSTOMERS
### ============================================

### 8.1 Quick Search by Name (Expected: 200 OK)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/customers/search/quick?keyword=Nguyen
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 8.2 Quick Search by Phone (Expected: 200 OK)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/customers/search/quick?keyword=0909
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 8.3 Quick Search - Short Keyword (Expected: 400 Bad Request)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/customers/search/quick?keyword=a
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ============================================
### 📝 HƯỚNG DẪN SỬ DỤNG
### ============================================
### 
### 1. Cài đặt VS Code extension "REST Client"
### 2. Chạy các request Login đầu tiên để lấy token
### 3. Copy token vào biến @adminToken, @cashierToken, @managerToken
### 4. Chạy các request test theo thứ tự
###
### ============================================
### ✅ CHECKLIST TEST
### ============================================
### 
### GET ALL:
### [ ] Admin get all customers → 200 OK
### [ ] Admin get with pagination → 200 OK
### [ ] Admin search customers → 200 OK
### [ ] Cashier get customers → 403 Forbidden
### [ ] No token → 401 Unauthorized
###
### GET BY ID:
### [ ] Get existing customer → 200 OK
### [ ] Get non-existent customer → 404 Not Found
###
### CREATE:
### [ ] Create valid customer → 200 OK
### [ ] Create without name → 400 Bad Request
### [ ] Create with invalid email → 400 Bad Request
### [ ] Create duplicate phone → 400 Bad Request
### [ ] Cashier create customer → 403 Forbidden
###
### UPDATE:
### [ ] Update existing customer → 200 OK
### [ ] Update non-existent → 404 Not Found
### [ ] Update duplicate phone → 400 Bad Request
###
### DELETE:
### [ ] Delete customer without invoices → 200 OK
### [ ] Delete customer with invoices → 400 Bad Request
### [ ] Delete non-existent → 404 Not Found
###
### CUSTOMER INVOICES:
### [ ] Get customer invoices → 200 OK
### [ ] Get invoices with pagination → 200 OK
### [ ] Get invoices non-existent customer → 404
###
### QUICK SEARCH:
### [ ] Search by name → 200 OK
### [ ] Search by phone → 200 OK
### [ ] Search short keyword → 400 Bad Request
###